    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meow yourself out of cyberspace!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro-futuristic journey full of music, puzzles, and cats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>CATWAVE95</strong>, an innocent cat finds itself trapped in cyberspace, controlled by a mischievous AI. Your mission: escape its grip while surviving puzzles, enemies, and challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simon on Steroids!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198540/extras/1d61dfe3fd86a29752bd535714e4be37.poster.avif?t=1734415116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198540/extras/1d61dfe3fd86a29752bd535714e4be37.webm?t=1734415116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198540/extras/1d61dfe3fd86a29752bd535714e4be37.mp4?t=1734415116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve dynamic musical puzzles</strong> inspired by classics like <i>Zelda: Ocarina of Time</i> and <i>Simon Says</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat enemy singers</strong> by shooting notes in the correct order.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore virtual screens</strong> that mimic retro Windows95 vibes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover hidden collectibles</strong> across 3 unique levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience an evolving story</strong> as the AI guide turns antagonist.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
